#: ../../project_and_asset_management/project_notes.rst:70
msgid ""
"A neat feature is the ability to create :doc:`markers</"
"cutting_and_assembling/markers>` from the timecodes in the notes. Select a "
"timecode (it does not matter if you select the additional text), and click "
"on |list-add|\\ :guilabel:`Create markers from selected timecodes`, and "
"Kdenlive creates a marker at that precise point in the timeline."
msgstr ""
"Una característica polida és la capacitat de crear :doc:`marcadors</"
"cutting_and_assembling/markers>` a partir dels codis de temps a les notes. "
"Seleccioneu un codi de temps (no importa si seleccioneu el text addicional), "
"i feu clic a |list-add|\\ :guilabel:`Crea marcadors a partir de codis de "
"temps seleccionats`, i el Kdenlive crearà un marcador en aquest punt precís "
"de la línia de temps."
